title: #92Noon! Live From Training Camp! Florio/Smith/Gleeman
description: PA and Nordo are live from TCO for the 2020 Vikings Training Camp! They are joined by Mike Florio of ProFootballTalk, Safey for the Vikings, Harrison Smith, as well as the weekly check in with Aaron Techie Gleeman with the WTA.
